Class GenericDialogAddin

java.lang.Object
jhd.ImageJAddins.GenericDialogAddin
public class GenericDialogAddin
extends java.lang.Object
GenericDialogAddIn adds instance methods for retrieving GenericDialog components

    • getPathField

      public GenericDialogAddin.PathField getPathField​(ij.gui.GenericDialog gd, java.lang.String labelName, java.lang.String panelName, java.lang.String textFieldName, java.lang.String buttonName)
      Call immediately after addFileField if you need to access the FileFields's methods.
      Pass null as arguments to retain respective component default names.
      Parameters:
      gd - The parent GenericDialog.
      labelName - assign this name to the FileField Label
      panelName - assign this name to the FileField Panel
      textFieldName - assign this name to the FileField TextField. In most cases this is the component of interest and should be named to access by name.
      buttonName - assign this name to the FileField Button
      Returns:
      a reference to the Objects in the prior addFileField
